duties_responsibilities.duty: Operate machinery to move materials around a facility for shipping, processing, and receiving.
Catalog, record, and organize materials received at the warehouse.
Fulfill customer orders by reading production schedules, order forms, and requisitions.
Locate, gather, and transport products to production workers, assembly line, or shipping areas.
Operate hand truck, cart, doilies, forklift, order-picker, and walkie to transport items.
Maintain a clean and safe work area.

education_certification.credential: High school diploma or General Education Degree (GED)
